      <div class="msgContentFrame">I agree. <br /> <br />In my opinion, the best route to skill from, <br />~1 - ~15+? <br /> <br />is by making (Copper Nugget) + (Copper Square x2) =&gt; Copper Buckle <br /> <br /> <br /> <br />Squares are purchasable from NPC at a reasonable rate (120g). Or you could synth them yourself if that is reasonable. 10+ this becomes 100exp/synth roughly. I really think it's unfortunate that this may be the best way to skill up safely past that point, but your best bet is prolly to accept that, grit your teeth, and grind it out. <br /> <br />13-14, I've been doing profit synths, though it's led me to leveling blacksmith and, to a lesser extent, goldsmith. I'm actually getting good exp while making a lot of money doing these. But I'm still probably leveling slower.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://www.ffxiah.com/player.php?id=19613" rel="external nofollow" title="www.ffxiah.com/player.php?id=19613"><b><span style="color:Red">Shamaya</b></span></a><a href="HTTP://shamayaasura.livejournal.com/" rel="external nofollow" title="shamayaasura.livejournal.com/"><b><span style="color:Red">, Asura</b></span></a></div></div>
